CNCP v1 23987
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#7299: expect vue3 implement sort of function like vnode.data.keepAlive for caching root instances like vue2 do.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:18.606255+00:00",
  "text": "expect vue3 implement sort of function like vnode.data.keepAlive for caching root instances like vue2 do.\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\n\r\nfor micro-frontend app use vue 2.* ，we can use Vnode.data.keepAlive to achive  caching root instances during switch tab.\r\nbut vue3 was not designed with that thought；\r\n```js\r\n// when micro app unmount\r\n  window.__CACHE_INSTANCE_BY_QIAN_KUN_FOR_VUE__ = cachedInstance;\r\n  const cachedNode = cachedInstance._vnode;\r\n  if (!cachedNode.data.keepAlive) cachedNode.data.keepAlive = true;\r\n\r\n  // when micro app mount\r\n  const cachedInstance = window.__CACHE_INSTANCE_BY_QIAN_KUN_FOR_VUE__;\r\n    // 从最初的Vue实例上获得_vnode\r\n    const cachedNode = cachedInstance._vnode;\r\n    instance = new Vue({\r\n        router,\r\n        store,\r\n        render: () => cachedNode,\r\n    });\r\n```\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\n\r\n```js\r\n//renderer.ts\r\n  const patch: PatchFn = (\r\n    n1,\r\n    n2,\r\n    container,\r\n    anchor = null,\r\n    parentComponent = null,\r\n    parentSuspense = null,\r\n    isSVG = false,\r\n    slotScopeIds = null,\r\n    optimized = __DEV__ && isHmrUpdating ? false : !!n2.dynamicChildren\r\n  ) => {\r\n...\r\n const { type, ref, shapeFlag } = n2\r\n    switch (type) {\r\n          ...\r\n          default:\r\n              if (shapeFlag & ShapeFlags.COMPONENT_KEPT_ALIVE) {\r\n                        processComponent(\r\n                          n1,\r\n                          n2,\r\n                          container,\r\n                          anchor,\r\n                          parentComponent,\r\n                          parentSuspense,\r\n                          isSVG,\r\n                          slotScopeIds,\r\n                          optimized\r\n                        )\r\n                      }\r\n}\r\n```\r\ncreate a new option  `if (shapeFlag & ShapeFlags.COMPONENT_KEPT_ALIVE) {}` to process keptAlive vnode;",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request"
  ],
